.sp
.nf
.ft C
hg diff foo.c
.ft P
.fi
.IP \(bu 2
.
compare two historical versions of a directory, with rename info:
.sp
.nf
.ft C
hg diff \-\-git \-\-from 1.0 \-\-to 1.2 lib/
.ft P
.fi
.IP \(bu 2
.
