.sp
.nf
.ft C
hg phabimport DREVSPEC... [OPTIONS]
.ft P
.fi
.sp
The patches are read and applied starting at the parent of the working
directory.
.sp
See \fBhg help phabread\fP for how to specify DREVSPEC.
